events.name: EV001少年の日の思い出自動実行

parameters:
Amel, the heir to the family fortune, Why do I have to do
something like this... Haven't any of you heard anything
from Father?

Clea: The request is to safely pass through the forest.
Other than that, we haven't heard anything from Father.

Amel, the heir to the family fortune, Are there any big
ones today?
Priestess Sophia: Oh my, is Nora-chan on your mind?

Amel, the heir to the family fortune, There's no way that's
true! I absolutely hate cowardly people!

Mage Relm: Please don't suddenly raise your voice! This is
why children can be troublesome...

Amel, the heir to the family fortune, Hmph, you're
probably the same kind of person, right?

Mage Relm: It takes quite some courage to speak like that
to a genius like me...!
Clea: Why are there people other than us here...?

Aspida Alliance's marauder: You're the son of an imperial
noble, huh? Shall we go together?
Clea: Please run away! We won't make it in time like this!

Thief Nora: Leave it to me, Amel-kun! I'll leave this to
Clea-san and the others!
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
